1. Use the 20-day moving average to judge trend: Price above MA20 = uptrend (only go long); Price below MA20 = downtrend (only go short);
2. Avoid range-bound markets: If price fluctuates within 5% of MA20, stay out of the market;
3. Case Study: In November 2025, crude oil futures broke above MA20â€” going long with the system brought a 12% profit.

